    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 12.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第12课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Goodbye and Good Luck.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "再见，一路顺风。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen, and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Where is Captain Allison going, and how?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "艾利森船长要去哪里？他将怎样去？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Our neighbor, Charles Allison, will sail from Portsmouth tomorrow.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们的邻居查尔斯·艾利森明天将从朴次茅斯启航。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "We'll meet him at the harbor early in the morning.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们一早会到港口为他送行。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "He will be in his small boat, Topsail.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他将乘坐自己的小船“涛波赛尔号”。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "Topsail is a famous little boat.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“涛波赛尔号”是一艘著名的小船。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "It has sailed across the Atlantic many times.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "它已经多次横渡大西洋。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Allison will set out at eight o'clock, so we'll have plenty of time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "艾利森将在8点钟出发，因此我们有充足的时间。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "We'll see his boat, and then we'll say goodbye to him.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们会参观他的船，然后向他告别。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "He will be away for two months.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他将离开两个月。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "We are very proud of him.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们为他感到非常自豪。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "He will take part in an important race across the Atlantic.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他将参加一场重要的横渡大西洋比赛。"
      }
    }
  ],
